5 Final Words_________________________________________________

Yes I did copy from the DeSmuME readme. I did not ask. If you
wish me to create my own readme from scrath please contact me
with your complaint. This software is to be used at your own
risk. I distribute this software with the intent of showing
how easy it was to create a working sms spam messaging app. I
however do not wish anyone to use this to actually spam other
people with this software. However I do ask, if you do use
this as such a tool, that you have a good reason harrass the
reciever of your messages. Also as my final word, if you use
this software as a spamming device you most likely WILL be
violating every line of Google's Terms of Service. So please
use this at your own risk. I have warned you!


5 tl;dr_______________________________________________________

Be responsible for your own actions. And think before you use
this software.